{
  "stem": "6777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in the later stages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already after Czerniakow's death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know that Adam Czerniakow, he had committed suicide after getting to know what the plans had been.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a job in the building department.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did all sorts of building jobs in and out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Out of the ghetto it was for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Inside it was ordered by the German Reich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not-- or this too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For example, they built a beautiful kindergarten, a place with playground equipment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they built a bridge across the Polish side of the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All sorts of jobs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had been architects, and they had been-- what do you call the engineers who build the roads and bridges?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and of course I'd been typing all this-- you know, the material necessary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because I was bilingual, when they had to present it to the Germans-- the plans plus the materials-- I had plenty of work to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't present the plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I typed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm the typing girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There had been two people going to the Germans to present it and sometimes the Germans came to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was engineer, Lichtenbaum yeah, son of the president.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then you may have heard about engineer, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Probably heard the name [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you also hear about the two painters [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's another story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, it was usually the young Lichtenbaum who went to the Germans to present the buildings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Building plans and the types-- what do you call this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't remember in English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you type out all the necessary timber and all the materials for the building?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a tin-- no, no not a tinder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a tinder--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
